# 3. System Philosophy

X2M is based on five principles:

### Predictive Modeling

Future states are estimated continuously.

### Multi-Dimensional Analysis

Systems are evaluated simultaneously across many variables.

### Continuous Feedback

Predictions are updated in real time.

### Recursive Optimization

Forecasts improve through iterative refinement.

### Cross-Domain Integration

Aviation, energy, infrastructure, and mobility systems can all utilize the same predictive framework.

